<link rel="alternate" type="application/json+oembed" href="http://www.tumblr.com/oembed/1.0?url=http://blog.getarkad.com/post/50348770974/lessons-learned-starting-our-first-business" title="Lessons Learned Starting Our First Business
We founded Arkad in August 2012 to provide companies with a simple investor and lender relationship tool. Initially, we started with venture-backed companies, but our broader goal was to change how..."/>
